                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, K</hi> 447). The prisoner was given into my custody—I told him the charge—he said, "Very well, I will go with you—I took him opposite the prosecutors window, which adjoins the Coach and Horses.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Was this the same night? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes; he used to come up my beat every morning to his work.</p>
